Package main.java.graphreduction.core

Class GraphController

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.graphreduction.core.GraphController
  • public class GraphController
extends java.lang.Object
    The graph controller is in charge of all the operations that are made on the graph (database). This includes operations like creating, dropping and altering the graph.
    Version:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Catherine Camier
